HEADWORD: Skinny
<hw>Skin"ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Consisting, or chiefly
consisting, of skin; wanting flesh.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Her <xex>skinny</xex>
lips.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He holds him with a <qex>skinny</qex> hand.</q>
<rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

